title: Smoky Chipotle BBQ Prawns
ingredients: ['3 cloves garlic, finely chopped', '2 chipotle chillies in adobo sauce, chopped', '1 lemon, juiced', '1 tablespoon olive oil', '1 tablespoon paprika', '1 teaspoon chopped fresh coriander', '1 teaspoon sea salt', '1/2 teaspoon cracked black pepper', '1/2 teaspoon crushed chillies', '1/4 teaspoon cayenne pepper', '900g raw medium prawns, peeled and deveined', '1 packet wooden skewers']
